<h1>About us</h1>
<h3>Our Origin Story: Born in the Heart of Pune</h3>
<p>Every great story in Pune starts with a good debate and a steaming cup of tea. Established in the bustling lanes of Pune, our cafe was born out of a simple dream: to create a space that feels like a backyard (angan) to every techie, student, and localite. We wanted to blend old-school legacy with modern-day cafe culture.</p>

<h3>The Brew & The Bite</h3>
<p>We don’t just serve coffee; we serve nostalgia and energy. From our signature, aromatic Puneri Amruttulya Chai and locally sourced Filter Coffee to modern espresso brews, we have something for every generation. Pair your drink with our freshly baked Bun Maska, classic Misal-Pav, or our fusion continental snacks.</p>

<h3>Our Mission & Values</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        <h3>The Katta Spirit:</h3>
        <p>We believe in the traditional Katta culture—a place where friends hang out for hours to discuss everything from politics to engineering assignments.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
        <h3>Locally Rooted:</h3>
        <p>We actively partner with regional farmers and local dairies to ensure our ingredients are as fresh as a morning walk on Tekdi.</p>
    </li>
</ul>

<h3>The Experience</h3>
<p>Step in for the aroma of freshly roasted beans, stay for the cozy retro-modern aesthetics. Whether you are looking for a quiet corner to plug in your laptop and work, or a lively spot to catch up with old friends, our cafe is designed to be your second home.</p>